data.text:
Drew Sidora

New collab from Real Housewives of Atlanta star Drew Sidora, a television and film actress, producer, entrepreneur, singer and philanthropist, is now exclusively available from HYPER iCONiC. Straight outta Chicago making iconic moves through her music and many roles including Disney’s “That’s So Raven” as Chantel, "The Game," as Lucy Avila in “Step Up," and over 20 additional feature films. Drew founded DREAMMAKERS, a vocal crusader for young girls and women, in 2013 giving back and supporting youth. She is dedicated to advocating for young women in need while also using her platform to entertain, transform, energize and inspire.
